Class MapEntry<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • MapEntry<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key type of entry.
    V - Value type of entry.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entry<K,V>
    public class MapEntry<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Entry<K,V>
    This class simulates an hash map entry. It has an constructor that creates an entry with given key and value. Then constructor sets the count number as 1.
